Static vs Dynamic Provisioning

@@ Static Provisioning
Storage Admin will Create PV and Developer Create PVC then PVC binds.

Problems: Manual & Slow, Difficult to Scale

@@ Dynamic Provisioning
Developer will Create PVC and Kubernetes Creates PV Automatically.

Benefits: Fast, Scalable & Automated.


@@ What is Dynamic Provisioning?
=>Automatic creation of Persistent Volumes using StorageClass when a PVC is created.

