Static Provisioning with NFS

Create PV.

apiVersion: v1
kind: PersistentVolume

metadata:
  name: nfs-pv

spec:
  capacity:
    storage: 20Gi

  accessModes:
  - ReadWriteMany

  nfs:
    path: /nfs-share/k8s
    server: 10.10.10.100

Apply:

kubectl apply -f pv.yaml

Create PVC.

apiVersion: v1
kind: PersistentVolumeClaim

metadata:
  name: nfs-pvc

spec:
  accessModes:
  - ReadWriteMany

  resources:
    requests:
      storage: 5Gi

Apply:

kubectl apply -f pvc.yaml

Verify:

kubectl get pv,pvc

Output:

PV      Bound

PVC     Bound
Intermediate Scenario

Deploy two Pods.

Both use same PVC.

Pod A:

echo "hello" > /data/test.txt

Pod B:

cat /data/test.txt

Output:

hello
